<!-- For an overview over all known types see: http://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mod%C3%A8le:Infobox_Musique_classique_(personnalit%C3%A9)#Charte_graphique -->
{{ConditionalMapping

| cases =
  {{Condition 
    | templateProperty = chart
    | operator = equals
    | value = danse
    | mapping = {{TemplateMapping | header = 0
                   | mapToClass = Dancer
                }}
  }}
  {{Condition
  | operator = otherwise
  | mapping = {{TemplateMapping | header = 0
                   | mapToClass = ClassicalMusicArtist
              }}
  }}

| defaultMappings =
  
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = nom | ontologyProperty = foaf:name }}
        {{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = nom autre | ontologyProperty = otherName }}
        {{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = légende | ontologyProperty = thumbnailCaption }}
        {{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = surnom | ontologyProperty = foaf:nick }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = nom de naissance | ontologyProperty = birthName }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = date de naissance | ontologyProperty = birthDate }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = lieu de naissance | ontologyProperty = birthPlace }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = date de décès  | ontologyProperty = deathDate }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = lieu de décès | ontologyProperty = deathPlace }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = lieux de résidence | ontologyProperty = residence }}
        {{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = activité principale | ontologyProperty = occupation }}
        {{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = tessiture | ontologyProperty = tessitura }}
        {{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = style | ontologyProperty = style }}
        {{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = genre | ontologyProperty = genre }}
        {{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = activités autres | ontologyProperty = otherOccupation }}
        {{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = lieux d'activité | ontologyProperty = city }}
        {{DateIntervalMapping
          | templateProperty          = années actives 
          | startDateOntologyProperty = activeYearsStartYear
          | endDateOntologyProperty   = activeYearsEndYear
        }}
        {{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = collaborations | ontologyProperty = collaboration }}
        {{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = éditeurs | ontologyProperty = recordLabel}}
        {{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = formation | ontologyProperty = education}}
        {{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = maîtres | ontologyProperty = mentor }}
        {{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = enseignement | ontologyProperty = educationPlace }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = élèves | ontologyProperty = disciple }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = ascendants | ontologyProperty = parent }}
        {{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = conjoints | ontologyProperty = spouse}}
        {{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = descendants | ontologyProperty = child }}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = famille | ontologyProperty = family}}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = récompenses | ontologyProperty = award}}
        {{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = distinctions | ontologyProperty = decoration}}
	{{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = web | ontologyProperty = foaf:homepage }}
        {{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = 	œuvres | ontologyProperty = created }}
        {{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = 	répertoire | ontologyProperty = created }}
        {{PropertyMapping | templateProperty = 	scènes | ontologyProperty = scene }}        
}}
